1
00:00:31,250 --> 00:00:33,125
I don't want to go just yet!

2
00:00:33,208 --> 00:00:35,125
Before the shuttle launches
and I leave this world,

3
00:00:35,208 --> 00:00:37,625
there's something I think
you outta know about me.

4
00:00:37,708 --> 00:00:39,250
[SHIDO]
What is it, Ririko?

5
00:00:39,333 --> 00:00:41,833
Everyone wants you to get really
good at flirting with Spirits

6
00:00:41,916 --> 00:00:44,000
so you can make them
fall in love with you.

7
00:00:44,083 --> 00:00:46,791
And you're supposed to get
better by practicing on me.

8
00:00:46,875 --> 00:00:48,375
[SHIDO]
Yeah, that's the plan.

9
00:00:48,458 --> 00:00:49,625
What about it?

10
00:00:49,708 --> 00:00:51,750
[RIRIKO]
Oh, it's just that I'm afraid.

11
00:00:51,833 --> 00:00:56,166
I'm afraid-- I might be
falling in love with you.

12
00:00:56,250 --> 00:00:57,041
It's true.

13
00:00:57,125 --> 00:00:58,375
We've known each other forever

14
00:00:58,458 --> 00:01:00,541
and you've always treated
me like a little sister,

15
00:01:00,625 --> 00:01:02,375
but do you think you
can start looking at me

16
00:01:02,458 --> 00:01:04,458
as a woman instead?

17
00:01:09,166 --> 00:01:12,291
This is the best day ever!

18
00:01:13,750 --> 00:01:15,125
Don't you worry about a thing.

19
00:01:15,208 --> 00:01:16,666
I'll even wave to
you from Jupiter,

20
00:01:16,750 --> 00:01:18,500
it's not super far away!

21
00:01:18,583 --> 00:01:20,916
Until next time, big brother!

22
00:01:23,375 --> 00:01:26,791
[SHIDO] All right! Ha, ha!

23
00:01:26,875 --> 00:01:28,291
I rock!

24
00:01:35,458 --> 00:01:36,708
[NARRATOR] Spirits.

25
00:01:36,791 --> 00:01:39,916
Mysterious girls appearing
from another world.

26
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,500
Should we fight against
their pure strength

27
00:01:41,583 --> 00:01:43,000
with weapons of war,

28
00:01:43,083 --> 00:01:45,208
or should we address
them with love?

29
00:01:45,291 --> 00:01:49,625
Now, mankind is faced with
the ultimate decision.

30
00:03:17,666 --> 00:03:19,375
[YOUNG ORIGAMI]
Dad! Mom!

31
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:25,041
Origami!

32
00:03:47,916 --> 00:03:49,083
Shin.

33
00:03:49,166 --> 00:03:51,625
[SHIDO]
Uh, yes, Reine?

34
00:04:05,458 --> 00:04:07,583
[KOTORI]
Are you daydreaming again?

35
00:04:07,666 --> 00:04:09,750
It's time to implement
Stage 2 of your training,

36
00:04:09,833 --> 00:04:11,291
so you better be ready.

37
00:04:11,375 --> 00:04:12,666
[SHIDO] Huh?

38
00:04:14,208 --> 00:04:16,208
This is training?

39
00:04:16,291 --> 00:04:18,125
Good afternoon, Shido.

40
00:04:18,208 --> 00:04:19,875
Is there something
I can help you with?

41
00:04:19,958 --> 00:04:21,583
No, thank you.

42
00:04:21,666 --> 00:04:23,458
[KOTORI]
What do you think you're doing?

43
00:04:23,541 --> 00:04:25,125
Quit wasting everyone's time.

44
00:04:25,208 --> 00:04:27,500
Hurry up and make her
fall in love with you.

45
00:04:27,583 --> 00:04:28,791
[SHIDO]
Do I have to?

46
00:04:28,875 --> 00:04:30,125
You ought to know by now

47
00:04:30,208 --> 00:04:32,375
that seducing a Spirit
is easier said than done.

48
00:04:32,458 --> 00:04:33,958
If you can't even
make a human love you,

49
00:04:34,041 --> 00:04:36,750
how do you expect to
convince a Spirit to?

50
00:04:37,958 --> 00:04:40,708
You're asking the wrong guy,
I'm not a stud.

51
00:04:40,791 --> 00:04:42,125
[KOTORI] We know!

52
00:04:42,208 --> 00:04:44,083
Just throw out a few compliments
and see what happens.

53
00:04:44,166 --> 00:04:48,750
If she responds well, we'll
give you further instructions.

54
00:04:48,833 --> 00:04:50,916
Um. Is there something
on your mind?

55
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:54,000
[SHIDO] Miss Okamine, that's
a cute outfit you're wearing!

56
00:04:54,083 --> 00:04:56,041
What? Goodness, you
really think so?

57
00:04:56,125 --> 00:04:58,208
Oh my, that is very
flattering of you.

58
00:04:58,291 --> 00:05:00,750
Oh, yes! It really
does look good!

59
00:05:00,833 --> 00:05:03,875
So does your hair!
And those sexy glasses!

60
00:05:03,958 --> 00:05:05,750
Perfect shoes!
Perfect stockings!

61
00:05:05,833 --> 00:05:07,625
Perfect attendance book! Heh.

62
00:05:07,708 --> 00:05:09,375
Shido? Is everything all right?

63
00:05:09,458 --> 00:05:12,250
[KOTORI] You got way too
into that. Stop being creepy!

64
00:05:12,333 --> 00:05:14,791
[TAMAE] I'm kind of busy right
now, so I'll see you in class.

65
00:05:14,875 --> 00:05:16,083
[SHIDO stammers]

66
00:05:16,166 --> 00:05:17,666
[REINE]
This can be fixed.

67
00:05:17,750 --> 00:05:18,791
All right.

68
00:05:18,875 --> 00:05:21,250
Listen closely and
do exactly as I say.

69
00:05:21,333 --> 00:05:22,416
[sighs]

70
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:23,666
Here's the truth.

71
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:24,916
I love homeroom.

72
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:27,375
I look forward to
going to it every day.

73
00:05:27,458 --> 00:05:30,833
Well that's nice to hear!
I'm so glad that you like it.

74
00:05:30,916 --> 00:05:32,083
[SHIDO]
The main reason is because

75
00:05:32,166 --> 00:05:34,750
I get to see you all the time.

76
00:05:34,833 --> 00:05:36,416
I can't help it.

77
00:05:36,500 --> 00:05:38,958
I think I've fallen
in love with you.

78
00:05:39,041 --> 00:05:41,041
Come on, don't say
such silly things!

79
00:05:41,125 --> 00:05:42,375
Honestly, I'm flattered,

80
00:05:42,458 --> 00:05:44,125
but students and teachers
can't love each other!

81
00:05:44,208 --> 00:05:46,500
No. Don't tell me that.

82
00:05:46,583 --> 00:05:50,083
I'm dead serious.
I want to marry you!

83
00:05:50,166 --> 00:05:54,666
[TAMAE]
You want to marry me?

84
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,250
Is it true?

85
00:05:56,333 --> 00:05:57,416
Once you're old enough to get
married, I'll be in my thirties.

86
00:05:57,500 --> 00:05:58,958
Is that ok? You need
to meet my parents!

87
00:05:59,041 --> 00:06:00,958
Daddy gets so protective
but I think he'll like you!

88
00:06:01,041 --> 00:06:02,250
He might even give us the house!

89
00:06:02,333 --> 00:06:03,625
Once you graduate
and get a decent job

90
00:06:03,708 --> 00:06:05,625
I can retire and
start having babies!

91
00:06:05,708 --> 00:06:07,875
Huh. We underestimated
the enthusiasm

92
00:06:07,958 --> 00:06:11,166
of 29-year old single women.
They make for easy targets.

93
00:06:11,250 --> 00:06:14,041
It'll be annoying if she gets
more involved than necessary.

94
00:06:14,125 --> 00:06:15,416
Hey Shido, we're done here,

95
00:06:15,500 --> 00:06:17,958
so make up some excuses and
get out of there pronto.

96
00:06:18,041 --> 00:06:19,416
I'm really sorry Miss Okamine,

97
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:22,416
I don't think I'm ready for
that level of commitment!

98
00:06:22,500 --> 00:06:24,208
We can start out in an
apartment and work our way up

99
00:06:24,291 --> 00:06:26,250
to a three-bedroom
condo with a backyard!

100
00:06:26,333 --> 00:06:27,625
And don't worry about
wedding planning!

101
00:06:27,708 --> 00:06:29,291
I've been saving up
for fifteen years!

102
00:06:29,375 --> 00:06:31,291
You can take care of
the DJ, I'll do the rest!

103
00:06:31,375 --> 00:06:33,541
Let's wait till Valentines Day,
that'd make it extra special!

104
00:06:33,625 --> 00:06:35,166
[KOTORI] You've found a
market with older women.

105
00:06:35,250 --> 00:06:36,208
Good to know.

106
00:06:36,291 --> 00:06:37,458
[SHIDO] Shut up!

107
00:06:37,541 --> 00:06:40,250
How can you be so calm
when I'm about to-- Ahh!

108
00:06:40,333 --> 00:06:42,750
Oh man. I'm sorry 'bout that.

109
00:06:45,916 --> 00:06:47,083
I'm alright.

110
00:06:47,166 --> 00:06:48,250
[KOTORI]
Perfect timing!

111
00:06:48,333 --> 00:06:50,000
Why don't you practice
with her, too?

112
00:06:50,083 --> 00:06:51,208
[SHIDO] Huh?!

113
00:06:51,291 --> 00:06:52,333
[KOTORI] She's around
the same age as you,

114
00:06:52,416 --> 00:06:53,458
so it'll be natural.

115
00:06:53,541 --> 00:06:54,833
Plus, even though
she's not a Spirit,

116
00:06:54,916 --> 00:06:56,875
she's a member of the AST.

117
00:06:56,958 --> 00:06:59,125
Doesn't seem like the type
to spread rumors either.

118
00:06:59,208 --> 00:07:00,666
Spread rumors
about what?

119
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:03,083
[KOTORI]
Just talk to her already!

120
00:07:03,166 --> 00:07:04,958
[SHIDO] Ugh.

121
00:07:05,041 --> 00:07:07,500
Uh... Hey Tobiichi!

122
00:07:07,583 --> 00:07:09,916
Those clothes look nice on you!
Where'd you get 'em?

123
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,458
[ORIGAMI]
It's a uniform.

124
00:07:11,541 --> 00:07:13,541
Come on, idiot, you have to
put in more effort than that.

125
00:07:13,625 --> 00:07:15,041
Again, with more feeling!

126
00:07:15,125 --> 00:07:16,208
[SHIDO]
I don't know how.

127
00:07:16,291 --> 00:07:18,875
[REINE]
Shin, follow my lead.

128
00:07:18,958 --> 00:07:21,250
To be honest,
I already know.

129
00:07:21,333 --> 00:07:23,625
I've known all about you
for quite a while now.

130
00:07:23,708 --> 00:07:24,625
I'm aware of that.

131
00:07:24,708 --> 00:07:26,708
Oh, is that so? Nice.

132
00:07:26,791 --> 00:07:28,916
I'm real glad we're in the
same class this semester.

133
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:31,625
In fact I watch you all the time
during class when you study.

134
00:07:31,708 --> 00:07:32,833
Yes, likewise.

135
00:07:32,916 --> 00:07:34,791
Is that so? How random.

136
00:07:34,875 --> 00:07:36,916
I also like sneaking into
your locker after school

137
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,541
to sniff your gym clothes.

138
00:07:38,625 --> 00:07:39,708
Same here.

139
00:07:39,791 --> 00:07:41,291
Okay. I wasn't expecting that.

140
00:07:41,375 --> 00:07:42,375
And why not?

141
00:07:42,458 --> 00:07:43,666
Who knew we'd have
so much in common.

142
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:46,541
So do you want
to go out with me?

143
00:07:47,916 --> 00:07:49,000
That came out of nowhere!

144
00:07:49,083 --> 00:07:50,166
Don't you think this
is a little sudden?

145
00:07:50,250 --> 00:07:51,875
I wouldn't mind.

146
00:07:51,958 --> 00:07:53,583
I wouldn't mind
going out with you.

147
00:07:53,666 --> 00:07:55,458
[SHIDO]
Uh... Cool.

148
00:07:55,541 --> 00:07:58,500
So you wanna, like, go somewhere
with me, something like that?

149
00:07:58,583 --> 00:08:00,083
[ORIGAMI]
Like a movie?

150
00:08:00,166 --> 00:08:03,208
I'm sorry, I assumed you were
asking me out on a date, Shido.

151
00:08:03,291 --> 00:08:04,458
Am I wrong?

152
00:08:04,541 --> 00:08:06,666
No, not at all, that's
exactly what I meant.

153
00:08:06,750 --> 00:08:07,583
[ORIGAMI] Good.

154
00:08:07,666 --> 00:08:08,708
[SHIDO] Dang it.

155
00:08:08,791 --> 00:08:10,416
That's exactly what I meant?

156
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:15,041
How come Reine didn't bail me
out of that one? I'm screwed!

157
00:08:15,125 --> 00:08:16,833
Uh... What's this?

158
00:08:16,916 --> 00:08:19,958
[ORIGAMI] For you,
because you like my uniform.

159
00:08:20,041 --> 00:08:21,125
[alarm sounds]

160
00:08:21,208 --> 00:08:21,916
[FEMALE ANNOUNCER]
Your attention, please.

161
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,166
This is not a drill.

162
00:08:23,250 --> 00:08:24,541
There have been precursory signs

163
00:08:24,625 --> 00:08:27,291
of an impending spatial
quake in this vicinity.

164
00:08:27,375 --> 00:08:28,458
Please evacuate...

165
00:08:28,541 --> 00:08:29,833
[ORIGAMI]
Something just came up. Bye.

166
00:08:29,916 --> 00:08:32,416
Hey! Wait a second!
Where are you going?

167
00:08:32,500 --> 00:08:34,250
[KOTORI] A spatial quake
is about to happen.

168
00:08:34,333 --> 00:08:36,708
Head back to the
Fraxinus for now.

169
00:08:36,791 --> 00:08:38,375
[SHIDO]
Do you think it's a Spirit?

170
00:08:38,458 --> 00:08:40,500
Yes. Princess.

171
00:08:40,583 --> 00:08:42,958
She'll be appearing
at your exact location.

172
00:08:43,041 --> 00:08:44,583
Raizen High School.

173
00:08:47,166 --> 00:08:53,541
[indistinct speaking
over intercom]

174
00:08:53,625 --> 00:09:03,166
[alarm sounds]

175
00:09:12,125 --> 00:09:13,083
They're on their way, now.

176
00:09:13,166 --> 00:09:14,416
Roger that.

177
00:09:26,291 --> 00:09:27,583
[FEMALE AST SOLDIER]
Here we go.

178
00:09:27,666 --> 00:09:29,333
The quake has started.

179
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:40,875
[crumbling sounds]

180
00:09:43,458 --> 00:09:45,750
[KOTORI] Consider
yourself lucky, Shido.

181
00:09:45,833 --> 00:09:48,291
The AST's CR-units are deadly,

182
00:09:48,375 --> 00:09:50,750
but they weren't built
for indoor combat.

183
00:09:50,833 --> 00:09:52,791
As long as Princess
remains inside the school,

184
00:09:52,875 --> 00:09:54,250
the AST will have a hard time

185
00:09:54,333 --> 00:09:56,416
interfering with
whatever you do.

186
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:58,000
[SHIDO]
With what I do?

187
00:09:58,083 --> 00:10:00,875
You know exactly what
I'm talking about.

188
00:10:00,958 --> 00:10:04,250
Relax, this is what you've been
training for the past week.

189
00:10:04,333 --> 00:10:06,291
You're as ready
as you'll ever be.

190
00:10:06,375 --> 00:10:08,041
You want to save the Spirit.

191
00:10:08,125 --> 00:10:10,708
Or am I wrong?

192
00:10:10,791 --> 00:10:12,250
[SHIDO] She's right.

193
00:10:12,333 --> 00:10:16,166
I don't ever want to see that
sad look on her face again.

194
00:10:16,250 --> 00:10:19,000
Kotori. You're absolutely
sure I can do this?

195
00:10:19,083 --> 00:10:21,000
[KOTORI] Yes. Just
believe in yourself.

196
00:10:21,083 --> 00:10:23,583
You represent a different way
of dealing with the Spirits,

197
00:10:23,666 --> 00:10:25,083
a more intimate method.

198
00:10:25,166 --> 00:10:26,666
Remember that.

199
00:10:26,750 --> 00:10:30,583
Be friendly with them, use sweet
talk, and make them fall for me.

200
00:10:33,958 --> 00:10:35,791
You're gonna do just fine.

201
00:10:35,875 --> 00:10:38,166
Besides, the Fraxinus
has got your back.

202
00:10:38,250 --> 00:10:39,583
Behold the pride of Ratatoskr,

203
00:10:39,666 --> 00:10:42,166
ready to respond to
any circumstance!

204
00:10:42,250 --> 00:10:45,125
With five marriages and five
divorces under his belt,

205
00:10:45,208 --> 00:10:46,458
the Love Master.

206
00:10:46,541 --> 00:10:49,291
"Bad Marriage" Kawagoe!

207
00:10:49,375 --> 00:10:50,541
Hey there!

208
00:10:52,083 --> 00:10:54,125
[KOTORI] It's the working girl's
favorite midnight client,

209
00:10:54,208 --> 00:10:56,291
CEO Mikimoto!

210
00:10:56,375 --> 00:10:58,541
Who doesn't love love?

211
00:10:58,625 --> 00:11:01,291
[KOTORI] Go after this lady's
fella and you'll regret it!

212
00:11:01,375 --> 00:11:03,041
Don't you dare piss her off.

213
00:11:03,125 --> 00:11:05,916
"Nail Knocker" Shiizaki!

214
00:11:07,458 --> 00:11:10,208
The man with no fewer
than a hundred wives.

215
00:11:10,291 --> 00:11:12,833
"Dimension Breaker" Nakatsugawa!

216
00:11:12,916 --> 00:11:14,541
A-okay!

217
00:11:14,625 --> 00:11:16,791
[KOTORI] Lastly, a woman
whose love is so strong,

218
00:11:16,875 --> 00:11:19,916
not even a silly restraining
order can keep her away.

219
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:22,833
"Deep Love" Minowa!

220
00:11:22,916 --> 00:11:24,791
Fantastic,
I'm relying on perverts.

221
00:11:24,875 --> 00:11:27,166
[REINE] Don't worry, everyone
is good at what they do.

222
00:11:27,250 --> 00:11:29,833
And that's only a portion
of the troops on our side!

223
00:11:29,916 --> 00:11:31,333
Just stay calm.

224
00:11:31,416 --> 00:11:32,666
Even if you die once,

225
00:11:32,750 --> 00:11:34,958
you can always start a new
game without a penalty.

226
00:11:35,041 --> 00:11:36,875
[SHIDO] I'm pretty sure
this isn't a game.

227
00:11:36,958 --> 00:11:38,708
[KOTORI] Have faith
in your little sister!

228
00:11:38,791 --> 00:11:40,416
Now get in there and flirt!

229
00:11:52,916 --> 00:11:54,250
[gasps]

230
00:11:59,958 --> 00:12:00,833
[SHIDO] Ahh!

231
00:12:02,791 --> 00:12:03,916
[SHIDO coughs]

232
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:04,958
Wait just a minute!

233
00:12:05,041 --> 00:12:06,583
I don't want to fight with you!

234
00:12:06,666 --> 00:12:09,333
Please, listen to me.

235
00:12:09,416 --> 00:12:10,875
[PRINCESS]
What's your name?

236
00:12:10,958 --> 00:12:13,208
And why are you following me?

237
00:12:13,291 --> 00:12:14,041
Because--

238
00:12:14,125 --> 00:12:16,125
[KOTORI]
Don't answer yet!

239
00:12:16,208 --> 00:12:17,166
[MINOWA]
There has been a change

240
00:12:17,250 --> 00:12:18,708
in the mental state
of the Spirit.

241
00:12:18,791 --> 00:12:20,458
[KAWAGOE]
Reaction analysis complete.

242
00:12:20,541 --> 00:12:22,833
[NAKATSUGAWA]
Displaying choices onscreen.

243
00:12:22,916 --> 00:12:24,416
[SHIDO]
My name is Shido Itsuka.

244
00:12:24,500 --> 00:12:26,125
I've come to save you!

245
00:12:26,208 --> 00:12:29,583
I'm just a passerby.
Please don't kill me!

246
00:12:29,666 --> 00:12:32,666
Before asking someone's name,
you should give your own.

247
00:12:34,625 --> 00:12:35,875
[KOTORI]
Well, there they are.

248
00:12:35,958 --> 00:12:37,666
Now everyone get to work!

249
